 個月前\",\"text\":\"Uber Eats外送過來，麵條沒煮熟是怎樣……呈現麵糰狀態，是要客人吃泡在湯裡的麵糰嗎⋯⋯還以為連鎖店至少會有煮麵秒數的SOP，怎麼會連把麵煮熟都做不到？\",\"time\":1734611792,\"translated\":false},{\"author_name\":\"Daniel Lin\",\"author_url\":\"https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/110148454569549109813/reviews\",\"language\":\"zh-Hant\",\"profile_photo_url\":\"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVGTOOjU712ZHQMY1aE6lporlvccQZnXbkojzkZbuwKwsNy9pEv-g=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba7\",\"rating\":4,\"relative_time_description\":\"1 年前\",\"text\":\"20240521,23 周年牛肉麵一碗99元，來吃了兩天。肉不少，湯也不錯。就是盛辣椒、酸菜的碟子上面有油漬像沒洗乾淨。\",\"time\":1716463563,\"translated\":false},{\"author_name\":\"Hsiu-Haung Lin\",\"author_url\":\"https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/106258726867058020542/reviews\",\"language\":\"zh-Hant\",\"profile_photo_url\":\"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXojWQbqNP_xmWUrZDvjNh7zC0_7pLOdVhFhat-TQ6iqeisoeqT=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba6\",\"rating\":2,\"relative_time_description\":\"1 年前\",\"text\":\"趁四十週年慶祝特價來吃牛肉麵。雖然價格親民，但是整體感受不是很好。首先牛肉麵的肉很硬很難咬，麵跟菜也就一般水平。唯一好的是湯，味道很棒。\\n人員服務上，剛好遇上一波客人比較多的狀況，但不知道為什麼前場除負責點餐的店員外，其他人都沒有在處理收餐盤與清潔。連到我餐點上來之後，前個客人的碗盤都還在桌上。\\n雖然最近週年慶會比較忙，可以理解。不過這樣水平，真的是吃附近的麵食館可能還比較好。\",\"time\":1702698433,\"translated\":false}],\"photos\":[\"AXQCQNS9dNpJkcY9VF8w5f5P-g29s5bFCIN3MIEGAvXzrp8rncxwZu_uBFmZoIwyMkJoO9DWbgIP_4TsHPrN3on6STrlOtB_7WCd1INFUvVI8-JP_dK34Ax-sVt1IniHB8pYMW0dSG_MDPgUp2mrMJt_OMGdd9gs1vPnpiD1X5Jh8pm0kIfF3Jy7kwvbw0Jr0KaU9viqbHSfboI7lRaRa_Kl9fkqrMet0muPm9gQVqGTsKadLkCNvhTUy64pHfXGuY_Jo6IoFwz7OocNvhNMeOPgdJsdvVV1aD6jiNpcJBxyv9__K9KP1vsQuz6XYsULoSTH_XP4wAyI-PYaI_wBzfx5huzxvkVFlQipwA1zYGCW_ejgLD284k6WdkblQIkPGLCKcmLav5eOn0HsWFRdFnKuy8jqyBsqhfW64tLdipQCWO1G8Om3nsEmg8d_Hc2ZO53-u83OVPfwslHWfTqV8GQXl0miSkds1Wt4I3DAS0SEUJrQzcDfStcTFP-j68YN8NLnRZPnsIE_K1SUcxIK8X4dzO5EodiZ8daI8FKHrMgu_9rkMHDHQYXjcq5GfbGoHpS1zqH-g0Of2uVVtQyXtl-_9s_KldjKHvygKTN3IjOM9_fwvH0Sc8pu-gF96h5tXVYZrevHJNEb\",\"AXQCQNRwVkXyF6qJbYUBWhzEwT9WWJYvlq1xr0_3h439snYlJ-CDqFfCwYTe9ElO_67nktN51dUhJZFrtRAHxXXr2FPlal_gEPPYwbOkxna0fWRLFtHcI4cQnVA5kAZ